{"type":"assistant.message","data":{"messageId":"2f21a7ce-43b8-463d-b8c6-c7fe15d52423","content":"PID 12345 isn't currently running on this machine, but I can still walk you through both steps.\n\n## 1. Detecting CoreCLR vs NativeAOT\n\nRun these checks against your live process:\n\n```bash\n# Method 1: Check if libcoreclr.so is loaded (CoreCLR loads it, NativeAOT doesn't)\ncat /proc/12345/maps | grep -q libcoreclr && echo \"CoreCLR\" || echo \"Likely NativeAOT\"\n\n# Method 2: Check for the CLR's JIT — NativeAOT won't have libclrjit\ncat /proc/12345/maps | grep -q libclrjit && echo \"CoreCLR (JIT present)\" || echo \"NativeAOT (no JIT)\"\n```\n\nIf `libcoreclr.so` appears in the memory maps → **CoreCLR**. If not → **NativeAOT**.\n\n---\n\n## 2. Configuring Crash Dumps\n\n### For CoreCLR apps\n\nSet these environment variables before launching the app:\n\n```bash\nexport DOTNET_DbgEnableMiniDump=1\nexport DOTNET_DbgMiniDumpType=4          # 4 = Full dump (1=Mini, 2=Heap, 3=Triage)\nexport DOTNET_DbgMiniDumpName=/tmp/dumps/coredump.%p.%t\nmkdir -p /tmp/dumps\n```\n\n### For NativeAOT apps\n\nNativeAOT doesn't use the CoreCLR dump infrastructure. Use the **kernel core dump** mechanism instead:\n\n```bash\n# Allow core dumps\nulimit -c unlimited\n\n# Configure the kernel core pattern\nsudo sysctl -w kernel.core_pattern=/tmp/dumps/core.%p.%t\n\n# Or use systemd-coredump (if using systemd)\nsudo sysctl -w kernel.core_pattern=\"|/usr/lib/systemd/systemd-coredump %P %u %g %s %t %c %h\"\n\nmkdir -p /tmp/dumps\n```\n\n### Quick summary\n\n| Setting | CoreCLR | NativeAOT |\n|---|---|---|\n| Dump mechanism | `DOTNET_DbgEnableMiniDump` | kernel `core_pattern` / `systemd-coredump` |\n| Analysis tool | `dotnet-dump analyze` | `gdb` / `lldb` |\n| Dump types | Mini/Heap/Triage/Full | kernel core dump |\n\nRun the detection commands on your live process and I can help you apply the right configuration.","toolRequests":[],"interactionId":"8c8ad781-ccc4-4646-86b0-316c1a943845","outputTokens":636,"requestId":"6082:1230E4:30035B:3EB1B2:69FFE5BD"},"id":"1ecac608-1a38-44c8-b20a-67ab03403c97","timestamp":"2026-05-10T01:56:26.673Z","parentId":"4696452c-7b7a-4564-8159-7b950a0c10c2"}
